videos.headline: Meyer takes field for first time since suspension
videos.description: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer sprints to the field for his first game back from suspension.

videos.headline: Ohio State opens game with 14-yard TD strike
videos.description: The Buckeyes cap off a 91-yard opening drive with a 14-yard touchdown strike from Dwayne Haskins to Parris Campbell.

videos.headline: Haskins on the money with 17-yard TD
videos.description: Buckeyes quarterback Dwayne Haskins fires a bullet to wide receiver Terry McLuarin for a 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Haskins drops dime for 37-yard TD
videos.description: Ohio State quarterback Dwayne Haskins drops a pretty 37-yard touchdown pass to Parris Campbell, their second scoring connection of the first quarter.

videos.headline: Tulane's 38-yard grab sets up goal-line TD
videos.description: Tulane quarterback Jonathan Banks lets one rip to Terren Encalade for a 38-yard gain, setting up a Darius Bradwell 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Haskins whips 31-yard TD to wide-open receiver
videos.description: Buckeyes quarterback Dwayne Haskins slings his fourth touchdown pass of the game, finding Binjimen Victor for a 31-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: OSU WR fights through jersey rip
videos.description: The bottom of Buckeyes WR Parris Campbell's jersey is ripped off by a Tulane defender en route to a 13-yard gain.

videos.headline: Buckeyes RB plunges into end zone
videos.description: Ohio State running back J.K. Dobbins takes the handoff eight yards and dives to the end zone for a Buckeyes' touchdown.

videos.headline: Haskins tosses 5th TD of 1st half
videos.description: Buckeyes quarterback Dwayne Haskins flings a beautiful back-shoulder, 14-yard touchdown pass to Austin Mack.

videos.headline: OSU's Martell struts into end zone
videos.description: Buckeyes quarterback Tate Martell fakes the defense and high-steps into the end zone for a 1-yard score.
